imdb.plot outline: Join our presenters, seasoned traveller, Jenny Powell and wine connoisseur, Olivier Magny as they set off on a culinary voyage of discovery through one of Europe's hidden treasures, Romania. Jenny and Olivier will meet local food producers, explore family-run vineyards and dine at the country's finest restaurants. This beautifully shot, entertaining and informative series offers a glimpse of the world as it used to be where man and nature work in perfect balance and will open up Romania to a new generation of tourists as well as providing fascinating facts for the more adventurous traveller. The journey takes our presenters from Maramures county to Transylvania and the Danube Delta, from Baia Mare, Arad and Cluj to Brasov, from the capital city Bucharest to Romania's oldest city Constanta.
